Type: Package
Package: nanoscopeAFM
Title: Load Atomic Force Microscopy Data Files
Version: 2.0.14
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Gredig", , "thomas.gredig@csulb.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5824-7626"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <thomas.gredig@csulb.edu>
Description: Reads and displays atomic force microscopy (AFM) image files 
    for analysis. The supported file formats include NanoSurf NID
    files, Bruker and VEECO NanoScope files, Park AFM files, and Asylum Research Igor Wavefiles. It
    can also flatten images, perform height-height correlation function analysis,
    line profiles, and basic data analysis. It can be used to analyze spectroscopy data for
    certain files.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://thomasgredig.github.io/nanoscopeAFM/
